_sText: I started this map back when I played surf_japan_v2 non stop. I wanted to create a japan like map. I got this far, but then I had no idea where the map would go next. I also lost my motivation to continue working on it. I would like someone to finish this map off, carry on where I finished. I would also like credit if you do complete this map. View more screenshots here! Please leave feedback if you are going to use and complete this map, along with links to the progress of the map.
